From f8536f39e235cb460b15d93376b72da00c44a6ca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sam <samuelngs@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 10 May 2026 20:24:10 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 07/15] chrome: inject chrome object via native V8
 FunctionTemplates

Injects chrome.app, chrome.runtime, chrome.csi, chrome.loadTimes
using native V8 API (FunctionTemplate/Object) instead of JS injection.
Avoids toString/prototype detection vectors used by bot detectors.

diff --git a/headless/BUILD.gn b/headless/BUILD.gn
index c17b97a6ea..977e7fd889 100644
--- a/headless/BUILD.gn
